de.hsrm.swt02.model

Class DataStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hsrm.swt02.model.DataStorage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class DataStorage
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Class to contain lists of Users, Workflows, Roles and Forms. Simplifies the Serialization, by saving data in one object of DataStorage and de-/serializing the complete object.
    Author:
    rhaba001
    See Also:
